{"tid":319493,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"老老豆豆, 如果DSE一年可以分兩次考有無得諗?","createTime":"2017-07-13T00:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T04:50:41.000Z","uid":84307,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27ab7ce7a238b58caff4d5ec4021e3b86b689e2b","tid":319493,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"自古至今, 由CEE, AL到依家DSE, 依D一年一度既考試一試定生死, 對考生同考生家人/朋友造成極大壓力, 相信各位巴絲都有體驗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反觀好多外國升大學試, 包括Provincial Exam, Advanced Placement, SAT(唔好講TOEFL, IELTS呢D), 好多都係一年可以考多過一次, 今次唔得都可以仲有下一次機會, 唔洗等足一年, 而且有選擇, 唔洗堆埋一齊一次過考曬6, 7科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於香港考生, 可以集中上半年(甚至早一年)考某幾科, 下半年考埋其餘幾科, 可以分開兩次, 唔洗短時間之內記曬咁多科既內容.  好似大學分sem咁, 4個月左右埋一次單, 萬一因為某D原因炒左科, 下半年都可以重take(高年級果D科另計)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本上, 小弟做左咁多年人都無試過要一次過考咁多內容, 而且每次考完, 兩個禮拜之內一定唔記得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我問過好多外國frd, 從佢地口中覺得無一個人會有咁大壓力(當然佢地考既內容比DSE少)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知如果真係要係香港實行一年考兩次DSE一定會有好多阻滯, 一定好多人屌曬鬼, 但如果慢慢推行, 長遠黎講應該唔係無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係有人會覺得一年考一次DSE係就係會好大壓力, 但可以俾個機會考生發展自己既潛能(麻煩唔好quote黃子華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 可以訓練出更多尖子, 而且傳統呢D野, 唔應該隨便改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知其他巴絲點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 一年考兩次DSE可以諗下喎<br />\n<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咪傻啦on9仔, 邊有想像中咁簡單"},{"pid":"44efe63730cd04c4c48ae578c22dd06b33eac534","tid":319493,"uid":12518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:10:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b18b8dc2cf010f7c914570fa3a0a5d734473db3","tid":319493,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"中英文有啲講運，呢兩科有得一年兩次就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c519bc4e489d2d8a4b0e9010da136ebc1e8cef","tid":319493,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251547544a97a32aad2f48b8179eb0cf0ba8d98f","tid":319493,"uid":124806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"GCEAL咪係呢套個mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}